    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno Domini millesimo centesimo vigesimo, nemine
                        imperante, pridie kalendas septembris, indicione octava. <placeName
                            ref="#places/80">Ferarie</placeName>, in loco qui dicitur
                            <placeName>Miciana</placeName>. Inter ceteras donaciones maxime illa
                        donacio principatum tenet que per salutem et remedium animarum conficitur et
                        per quam vita heterna speratur. Unde profiteor me ego <persName
                            key="#childOf  #Offersio/donatio #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fruits/vegetables #Saltworks #Salt"
                                ><name ref="Berta/Palmera">Berta Palmera</name></persName> zelo Dei
                        quo acta, pro remedium anime mee meorum parentum profiteor me donare nata et
                            <rs key="#childOf">filia</rs> scilicet de <persName key="#parentOf"
                                ><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> de <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus/Staniu">Dominico Staniu</name></persName> de
                            <placeName key="#Casalia #Saltworks #Salt #Ports">Cloza
                            Minore</placeName>, per hanc <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">donacionis
                            paginam</rs>, profiteor me donare tibi presenti domno <persName
                            key="#Priors #Churches" ref="#people/4018">Ugoni</persName> religioso
                            <rs key="#Priors">priori</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Priors" ref="#juridical_persons/2098">Sanctae
                            Agathe</orgName> et per te in venerabili <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Churches #Priors #Offersio/donatio"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti de Lairone</orgName>, in
                        quo Deo gubemante preesse videtur domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/3568">Heinricus</persName>
                        gloriosus <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> suisque successoribus abbatibus in
                        perpetuum. Hoc est quantumcumque mihi pertinet per successionem patris mei
                        Martini de Dominico Staniu de suprascripta Cloza Minore, videlicet <rs
                            key="#Casalia">casalem</rs> unum in suprascripta Cloza iuxta latus
                                <persName><name ref="Leo/Staniu">Leonis Staniu</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Dominicus/Staniu">Domin[ic]o
                            Staniu</name></persName>, et terciam partem de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">clusuria</rs> una cum <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">horto</rs> uno iuxta latus similiter Leonis
                        Staniu et Domini[co] Staniu, et tres <rs key="#Saltworks #Salt">salinas</rs>
                        que sunt posite non longne a <rs key="#Ports">porto</rs> de Cloza iuxta
                        latus predicti Leonis et Dominici Staniu, cum ingresibus et hegresibus earum
                        et cum omnibus a suprascriptis rebus pertinentibus. Ut modo a presenti die
                        liceat tibi suprascripto priori tuisque successoribus habere tenere
                        possidere iure dominii predicti monasterii in perpetuum unde investitorem
                        tibi do Petrum de Sancta Agathe qui te investiat de suprascriptis rebus in
                        vice ecclesie in perpetuum. Quin eciam spondeo ego antefata Berta Palmeria
                        filia quondam Martini de Dominico Staniu pro me et pro meis filiis et
                        heredibus hamc donacionis paginam firmam tenere et conservare et defensare
                        et torizare tibi suprascripto domino Ugoni priori in vice ecclesiae Sancti
                        Benedicti et per persona antifati abbatis suisque successoribus, sub pena
                            <rs key="#Penalty">auri unciarum trium</rs> et soluta pena in sua stet
                        firmitate. Quam scribere rogavi <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Dominicus/notarius"
                                >Dominicum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs>, sub die, mensis et indicione suprascripta.
                        + Signum manus suprascripte Berte donatrice firmavit. +++++++ Signa et
                        nomina <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>: <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes/Balbus">Iohannes Balbus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="/Infans/de Sancto Donatho"
                                >Bonus Infans</name></persName> de Sancto Donatho, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Vitalis/de Sette"
                                >Vitalis</name></persName> de Sette, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Iohannes/Bonus/de Berardo"
                                >Iohannes Bonus</name></persName> de <persName><name ref="Berardus"
                                >Berardo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Domninus/de Sancto Felice"
                                >Donino</name></persName> de Sancto Felice, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Petrus/de Contrapatho"
                                >Petrus</name></persName> de Contrapatho, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Benedictus/de Marcaria"
                                >Benedicto</name></persName> de <placeName>Marcaria</placeName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Petrus/ de Sancta Agatha">Petrus</name></persName> de Sancta
                        Agatha testes. Ego Dominicus divino nutu notarius rogatus a suprascripta
                        Berta donatrice vinculis scripturarum alligandam adnexui. </ab>
                </div>
